### List prescriptions
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/prescriptions?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Create prescription (with medications)
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/prescriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-10",
  "consultationId": 1,
  "medications": [
    { "medicationId": 1, "quantity": 2, "instructions": "Tomar después de comer" },
    { "medicationId": 2, "quantity": 1, "instructions": "Una vez al día" }
  ]
}

### Get prescription
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/prescriptions/1
Accept: application/json

### Update prescription
PUT http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/prescriptions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-11",
  "consultationId": 1,
  "medications": [
    { "medicationId": 1, "quantity": 3, "instructions": "Tomar con agua" }
  ]
}

### Delete prescription
DELETE http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/prescriptions/1


